data.description: This home features great curb appeal and is perfectly landscaped. There's a cozy Living Room that flows into a Dining Area that has high-end custom flooring. Just behind that you have a spacious kitchen with a large center island that opens to a spacious Family Room. The Primary Suite sits at the rear of the property, which allows you to watch the golfers "play through" without leaving your bed! It has an en-suite bathroom as well. With 2 additional bedrooms, there's plenty of room for the kids to come and spend time with you. The backyard, which backs to the golf course, has a nice metal patio cover that goes the length of the patio as well as golf ball reflecting screens on the windows on the "play-through side of the house. Don't miss the great opportunity to own this home with a Premium lot that backs directly to the golf course.         Four Seasons Hemet is a luxury playground for 55+ youngsters! It is situated around an 18-hole championship golf course. There are tennis courts, bocce ball, and shuffleboard courts, an exercise room, a computer room, a library, a game room, a crafts room, a hair salon, an Olympic size pool, a spa, an outdoor picnic area, an outdoor event area, and clubs of all types. The Lodge also houses a cafe, movie theatre, billiards room, and community room. This all sits behind security gates that are manned/monitored 24 hours a day.
